# Thoth local data.
#
# The markdown source-of-truth (MEMORY.md, LESSONS.md, skills/) can be
# committed alongside the repo. Everything under `index/` is derivable and
# should never be tracked.
.thoth*/
!.thoth/
!.thoth/MEMORY.md
!.thoth/LESSONS.md
!.thoth/skills/

# Stray local databases from prototype runs
/identifier.sqlite
/identifier.sqlite-*
# MCP local config
.mcp.json

# Secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Build artifacts
*.profraw
*.profdata
